Build-Depends: cmake, debhelper-compat (= 13), libboost-dev <!nocheck>, libhowardhinnant-date-dev, libsqlite3-dev, sqlite-modern-cpp-dev, zlib1g-dev
Description: C++ library to allow access to DJ record database formats The libdjinterop library is a C++ library that allows access to database formats used to store information about DJ record libraries. . This library currently supports: - Engine Library, as used on "Prime"-series DJ equipment.
